<refsect2 id="rc-gui-style-set-color-style" role="function">
<title>rc_gui_style_set_color_style ()</title>
<indexterm zone="rc-gui-style-set-color-style"><primary>rc_gui_style_set_color_style</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting><link linkend="void"><returnvalue>void</returnvalue></link>                rc_gui_style_set_color_style        (<parameter>const <link linkend="RCGuiColorStyle"><type>RCGuiColorStyle</type></link> *style_data</parameter>);</programlisting>
<para>
Set the color style of the player by given data.
</para><variablelist role="params">
<varlistentry><term><parameter>style_data</parameter>&#160;:</term>
